723371f-a.title: Manhattan: Spring Street - Sullivan Street
723371f-a.text:
202 to 206 (left to right) Spring Street, at, adjoining and west of
the S.W. corner of Sullivan Street, as seen across the clearance on the
north side of the street. No. 202, the 27-story house at the corner, is
a frame building with a brick front.
May 20, 1937.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.

723372f-a.title: Manhattan: Spring Street - Sullivan Street
723372f-a.text:
Spring Street, east from Sullivan Street. In the background appears
a portion of the Sixth Ave. Elevated Line on West Broadway.
May 20, 1937.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
